       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    PSI56102.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA PSI56102.
      *
      *     Download
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE PSI56102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *    EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDWN00 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      * TABELA PSHEADER  (REG HEADER)
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDHEADER END-EXEC.
      * TABELA PSFICHEIR (REG FICHEIR)
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDFICHEI END-EXEC.
      * TABELA PSFICHREL (REG FICHREL)
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDFICHRL END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY PSCV5610.
       COPY PSCV5611.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY AQCL0001.
      * COPY CONVERS�O DE DATAS
       COPY AQCW0005.
       COPY AQCW0009.
       COPY VIAW0005.
      *     OBTEM NOME DO CLIENTE NA BANKA
       COPY SXCL0380.
       COPY SXCL0002.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY PSCK0001.
       COPY PSCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-PSDOWNL                  PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSDOWNL'.
           05 CON-PSHEADER                 PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSHEADER'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME                  PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSI56102'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARI�VEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DATA8    PIC 9(08) VALUE ZEROES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE PSI56102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO PSCV5610-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV5610-ASE       TO PSCV5611-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'INICIO PSI56102'       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV5610-ADE       TO PSCV5611-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2050-VALIDA-DADOS
                 THRU 2059-VALIDA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF

           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2050-VALIDA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-VALIDA-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-VALIDA-DADOS'     TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV5610-ORNCLI
             TO PSFICHREL-FRNCLI
           MOVE PSCV5610-ORNFIC
             TO PSFICHREL-FRNFIC
      * CONVERTE DATA DE X(10) PARA 9(08)
           MOVE PSCV5610-ORDINT          TO AQCW0005-DTX10
           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT
           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98            TO WS-DATA8
           MOVE WS-DATA8                 TO PSFICHREL-FRDINT

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT FRNOMEO
                  , FRNOMEF
                  , FRCHKSO
                  , FRCHKSC
                  , FRBIBLI
                  , FRFORM
               INTO :PSFICHREL-FRNOMEO
                  , :PSFICHREL-FRNOMEF
                  , :PSFICHREL-FRCHKSO
                  , :PSFICHREL-FRCHKSC
                  , :PSFICHREL-FRBIBLI
                  , :PSFICHREL-FRFORM
               FROM PSFICHREL
              WHERE FRNCLI = :PSFICHREL-FRNCLI
                AND FRDINT = :PSFICHREL-FRDINT
                AND FRNFIC = :PSFICHREL-FRNFIC
              FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE PSFICHREL-FRNOMEO
                   TO PSCV5611-ORNOMEO
                 MOVE PSFICHREL-FRNOMEF
                   TO PSCV5611-ORNOMEF
                 MOVE PSFICHREL-FRCHKSO
                   TO PSCV5611-ORCHKSO
                 MOVE PSFICHREL-FRCHKSC
                   TO PSCV5611-ORCHKSC
                 MOVE PSFICHREL-FRBIBLI
                   TO PSCV5611-ORBIBLI
                 MOVE PSFICHREL-FRFORM
                   TO PSCV5611-ORFORM
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPDINT-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNFIC-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2059-VALIDA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-ONTEM-DADOS'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV5610-ORNCLI
             TO PSFICHEIR-FCNCLI
           MOVE PSCV5610-ORNFIC
             TO PSFICHEIR-FCNFIC
      * CONVERTE DATA DE X(10) PARA 9(08)
           MOVE PSCV5610-ORDINT          TO AQCW0005-DTX10
           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT
           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98            TO WS-DATA8
           MOVE WS-DATA8                 TO PSFICHEIR-FCDINT
      **R
           MOVE ZEROES                   TO PSFICHEIR-FCNREG
      **R

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT FCNOMEF
               INTO :PSFICHEIR-FCNOMEF
               FROM PSFICHEIR
              WHERE FCNCLI = :PSFICHEIR-FCNCLI
                AND FCDINT = :PSFICHEIR-FCDINT
                AND FCNFIC = :PSFICHEIR-FCNFIC
      **R
                AND FCNREG = :PSFICHEIR-FCNREG
      **R
              FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
              WITH UR
           END-EXEC

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'APOS PSFICHEIR    '    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSFICHEIR-FCNCLI'      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSFICHEIR-FCNCLI        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSFICHEIR-FCNFIC'      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE PSFICHEIR-FCNFIC        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'PSFICHEIR-FCDINT'      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE PSFICHEIR-FCDINT        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'SQLCODE'               TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
              MOVE SQLCODE                 TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNCLI-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPDINT-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNFIC-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-MSG
                 ELSE
                    PERFORM 2150-OBTEM-SITUACAO
                       THRU 2150-OBTEM-SITUACAO-EXIT
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPDINT-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNFIC-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

      **R
           MOVE SPACES TO PSCV5611-ORNMCLI
      **R  PERFORM 4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
      **R     THRU 4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT.

       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS        TO SXCL0380-VERSAO
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME                TO SXCL0380-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-NOME-CLI      TO SXCL0380-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID          TO SXCL0380-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO SXCL0380-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO SXCL0380-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK          TO SXCL0380-RCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO SXCL0380-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO SXCL0380-APTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-VMSG         TO SXCL0380-HCLI.
           MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL         TO SXCL0380-VNCR.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO SXCL0380-CLBAL.
           MOVE PSCV5610-ORNCLI            TO SXCL0380-CLNCLI.

           CALL SXCL0380-ROTINA         USING SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                              SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE SXCL0380-RCODE             TO AQCW0009-RCODE.

           PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
              THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

           IF AQCL0001-COM-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-N-EXISTS TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-MSG
           ELSE
              MOVE SXCL0380-DWT OF SXCL0380-WT OF SXCL0380-DATA(1)
                                           TO PSCV5611-ORNMCLI
           END-IF.
      *
       4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2150-OBTEM-SITUACAO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2150-OBTEM-SITUACAO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-OBTEM-SITUACAO'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV5610-ORNCLI            TO PSHEADER-HRNCLI.
           MOVE WS-DATA8                   TO PSHEADER-HRDINT.
           MOVE PSCV5610-ORNFIC            TO PSHEADER-HRNFIC.

           EXEC SQL
             SELECT HRSITU
                  , HRSITR
               INTO :PSHEADER-HRSITU
                  , :PSHEADER-HRSITR
               FROM PSHEADER
              WHERE HRNCLI = :PSHEADER-HRNCLI
                AND HRDINT = :PSHEADER-HRDINT
                AND HRNFIC = :PSHEADER-HRNFIC
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-PSHEADER               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-'                 TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSHEADER-HRNCLI'       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSHEADER-HRNCLI         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSHEADER-HRNFIC'       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE PSHEADER-HRNFIC         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'PSHEADER-HRDINT'       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE PSHEADER-HRDINT         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'SQLCODE'               TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
              MOVE SQLCODE                 TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE PSCV5610-ORNCLI
                   TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI
                 MOVE PSCV5610-ORDINT
                   TO PSCV5611-ORDINT
                 MOVE PSCV5610-ORNFIC
                   TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC
                 MOVE PSFICHEIR-FCNOMEF
                   TO PSCV5611-ORNOMEF
                 MOVE PSHEADER-HRSITR
                   TO PSCV5611-ORSITR
                 MOVE PSHEADER-HRSITU
                   TO PSCV5611-ORSITU
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNCLI-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPDINT-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-RPNFIC-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5611-ORNFIC-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2150-OBTEM-SITUACAO-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'FIM PSI56102'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV5611-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE PSCV5611-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV5611-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
       COPY VIAP0016.
      * COPY CONVERS�O DE DATAS
       COPY AQCP0005.
       COPY AQCP0009.
